Malaysia April trade data due on Friday - Bernama . Malaysia ' s monthly trade data for April will be released on Friday , the national news agency Bernama said on Thursday . Bernama , which disseminates the figures , said the Statistics Department data will be released at 1200 local time ( 0400 GMT ) . A Reuters poll of nine economists had put an average trade deficit of 273 . 6 million ringgit for April . Malaysia posted a trade surplus of 1 . 75 billion ringgit in March . - - Kuala Lumpur newsroom ( 603 - 206 2323 ) 
